182
00:09:38,704 --> 00:09:40,360
Hello, Director Yao.

183
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,519
Yuheng.

184
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,799
Regarding the August

185
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:46,759
