187
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:51,360
We're just missing you.

188
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,360
Okay, I'll head over now.

189
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,400
Alright.

190
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:05,039
Sorry, I'm a bit busy today.

191
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:07,039
