192
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:09,240
Busy?

193
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:11,840
Busy trying to become a manager
in Division One?

194
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,440
Have you heard that Ji Yuheng
from the Compliance Department

195
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,799
